---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About IKAI | Energy Engineering Consultancy" description="Learn about IKAI Energy Consulting, an independent Melbourne-based power systems and grid connection consultancy.">
<section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><span class="eyebrow gold">About IKAI</span><h1>Engineering judgement that moves projects forward.</h1><p class="lead">IKAI is an Australian engineering consultancy delivering practical solutions for renewable energy and power systems.</p></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="container grid-2 about-intro reveal"><h2>Technical excellence, guided by purpose.</h2><div><p class="lead">The name IKAI is inspired by <em>ikigai</em>—the idea of meaningful purpose. For us, that means applying engineering expertise to help build an energy system worth believing in.</p><p>IKAI supports developers, investors and asset owners in navigating technical complexity, managing project risks and delivering successful energy infrastructure projects across Australia.</p></div></div></section>
<section class="section section-soft"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><div><span class="eyebrow">How we work</span><h2>Focused on what matters.</h2></div></div><div class="grid-3"><article class="value card reveal"><b>01</b><h3>Clarity</h3><p>IKAI turns complex technical issues into clear decisions, priorities and actions.</p></article><article class="value card reveal"><b>02</b><h3>Integrity</h3><p>Independent advice, transparent communication and accountable engineering judgement.</p></article><article class="value card reveal"><b>03</b><h3>Purpose</h3><p>Engineering solutions that support reliable, efficient and sustainable energy systems.</p></article></div></div></section>
<section class="section founder"><div class="container grid-2"><div class="founder-visual reveal"><img src="/images/ikai-logo-square-navy.png" alt="IKAI emblem"/></div><div class="reveal"><span class="eyebrow">Why IKAI</span><h2>Focused on successful project delivery.</h2><p class="lead">IKAI combines technical excellence with practical project delivery. Every engagement is focused on providing clear advice, efficient engineering solutions and outcomes that support long-term project success.</p><div class="credentials"><span>Independent technical advice</span><span>Deep power systems expertise</span><span>Practical engineering solutions</span><span>Strong stakeholder coordination</span></div><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-dark">Start a conversation ↗</a></div></div></section>
<section class="cta-section"><div class="container cta-inner"><div><span class="eyebrow gold">Work with us</span><h2>Independent expertise for your next energy project.</h2></div><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact IKAI ↗</a></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
<style>.about-intro{align-items:start}.about-intro p+p{margin-top:22px;color:var(--muted)}.value{padding:38px}.value b{color:var(--gold)}.value h3{font-size:1.6rem;margin:45px 0 14px}.value p{color:var(--muted)}.founder-visual{background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--radius);display:grid;place-items:center;min-height:500px;overflow:hidden}.founder-visual img{width:82%}.founder h2{margin:20px 0 24px}.founder .lead{margin-bottom:28px}.credentials{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin:30px 0}.credentials span{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:14px;font-weight:700}.cta-section{background:var(--navy-900);padding:90px 0}.cta-inner{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:40px}.cta-inner h2{color:#fff;margin-top:14px}@media(max-width:700px){.credentials{grid-template-columns:1fr}.cta-inner{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}}</style>
